nl.esciencecenter.xenon.adaptors.ftp

Class FtpQuery<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.esciencecenter.xenon.adaptors.ftp.FtpCommand
      • nl.esciencecenter.xenon.adaptors.ftp.FtpQuery<T>

  • public abstract class FtpQuery<T>
extends FtpCommand
    Wrapper class for executing a single operation on an FTPClient that returns a result. The wrapper takes care of checking the status after execution and throwing an exception if necessary.
